'''''Hacienda''''' is the eighth studio album by [[Grammy Award]] nominated [[Jazz]] band [[Jeff Lorber|Jeff Lorber Fusion]]. ''Hacienda'' was nominated for [[Grammy Award for Best Pop Instrumental Album|Best Pop Instrumental Album]] at the [[56th Annual Grammy Awards]] (held on January 26 2014) losing to [[Herb Alpert]] for ''[[Steppin' Out (Herb Alpert album)|Steppin' Out]]''.

==Track listing==
All tracks composed by Jeff Lorber; except where indicated
