# "Solar Wind" - 4:58 (Featuring [[Larry Koonse]])  
# "King Kong" - 5:41 ([[Frank Zappa]]) (Featuring [[Jean-Luc Ponty]])
# "The Steppe" - 5:20 
# "Hacienda" - 5:31 
# "Fab Gear" - 4:54 
# "Raptor" - 5:46 
